    {"type":"text","id":"t_horn","x":785,"y":640,"width":220,"height":20,"text":"12V 喇叭 (可选)","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"strokeColor":"#e5e5e5","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"middle","containerId":"horn","originalText":"12V 喇叭 (可选)","autoResize":true},
    {"type":"text","id":"t_horn_detail","x":790,"y":670,"text":"12V→喇叭+  喇叭-→MOSFET D\nGPIO12→100Ω→MOSFET G  S→GND\n(共用蜂鸣器GPIO, IRLZ44N)","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":1,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","originalText":"12V→喇叭+  喇叭-→MOSFET D\nGPIO12→100Ω→MOSFET G  S→GND\n(共用蜂鸣器GPIO, IRLZ44N)","autoResize":true},

    {"type":"text","id":"note","x":40,"y":750,"text":"注意事项:\n• 12V电源GND、5V电源GND、ESP32 GND 必须共地\n• MOSFET: IRLZ44N (逻辑电平, 3.3V可完全导通) 或 AO3400 (贴片)\n• 不加10kΩ栅极下拉 (已修复PWM模式bug)\n• 雷达5V取电, 文档确认支持5V","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":1,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","originalText":"注意事项:\n• 12V电源GND、5V电源GND、ESP32 GND 必须共地\n• MOSFET: IRLZ44N (逻辑电平, 3.3V可完全导通) 或 AO3400 (贴片)\n• 不加10kΩ栅极下拉 (已修复PWM模式bug)\n• 雷达5V取电, 文档确认支持5V","autoResize":true}
